  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Strengthen Mauritania&#x2019;s Preparedness, Response, and Resilience to Climate Change Induced Natural Disasters</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project&apos;s overall objective is to prevent climate change induced internal displacement by strengthening the disaster risk reduction response capacities in Mauritania. Institutional capacities are being strengthened by reforming the operational framework of Mauritania&apos;s national disaster response and risk reduction strategy and by establishing a regional contingency plan for the Guidimakha region.</narrative>
  </description>
